    <thetext>Usecase:
Precondition:  Change the Bookmark decorator to add decorations as non-volatile
1) Create a logic diagram
2) add a circuit
3) add a LED in the circuit
3) add a bookmark to the LED
4) Select the circuit
5) press CTRL+C
6) paste into MS Word

- At this point the bookmark decorator is not visible on the pasted copy of the diagram.

Expected behavior is that non-volatile decorators will be copied when preforming a copy/paste operation.</thetext>
